19 The signage shall include a brief message encouraging students experiencing
20 emotional distress to seek help as well as an explanation that the hotline is free,
21 confidential, and available twenty-four hours a day and seven days a week.
22 (b) The signage shall also include information about Louisiana988.org and
23 an explanation that additional information and resources, including the ability to chat
24 online, are available at this website.
25 (c) The signage shall be placed in locations easily visible to students such as
26 school entrances and exits, student common areas, school counselor offices, school
27 nurse offices, near restrooms and locker rooms, and digital school bulletin boards if
28 available."
